NEVER BUY in DOWN-trend

Break-out with Huge vol =>Change in trend.


Candles:

Candles Bullish: Should be end of at DOWN-TREND

Bullish Engulfing Pattern - 1st Red, 2nd Big Green
Morning Star- Red, Doji, Big Green
Hammer - Any Color
Inverted Hammer


Bearish: Should be at end of UP-TREND

Bullish Engulfing Pattern - 1st Green, 2nd Big Red
Evening Star- Green, Doji, Big Red
Hanging Man
Shooting Star


Moving Avg: Lagging

MACD: Moving Avg Convg. Divg.

RSI:
Above 60: Buy | Supp@ 60
Below 40: Sell


Strategy: 

MACD+RSI
1. MACD - Bullish Crossover
2. RSI - 60+

Trgt: 3% to 5% in 10 Days
SL: Median of breakout Candle (5-6 lower)

Bollinger Bands:
BB Squeeze (mini. 1 month)

Fibo:
Lowest to highest


Patterns:

UP Flag / FLAG POLE:
Up move, Sidemove, Close above Resis., 
Price Trgt: pole = Upmove
Time trgt: Sidemove Days(cloth) /3

HEAD & Shoulder:
Price Trgt: Head to Neckline = Upmove
Time trgt: Start of Neck till Break-out/3

Double Bottom: {Big Green Candle at 2nd Supp}
Price Trgt: Bottom level /2 = Upmove
Time trgt:  1st bottom till Break-out Candle (2nd Supp)/3
